EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
======================================================================

AERP-220 is an adaptive mobility platform architecture integrating
STARFRAME Mobility Lattice structural intelligence, distributed
structural cognition, Intelligent Wheel Organisms, AFAT-A220
predictive aerodynamic systems, NEO CORE Thermal/Hydraulic/Air Nodes,
X2M predictive intelligence and advanced energy ecosystem management.

The platform is conceived as a Living Mechanical Organism.

Rather than operating as a collection of isolated subsystems,
AERP-220 integrates structure, propulsion, sensing, aerodynamics,
thermal regulation, predictive intelligence and human-centered
control into a unified adaptive mobility architecture.

